#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1367
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "For example, entering <userinput>gg:konqueror</userinput> into the "
#| "Location Bar and pressing &Enter; will ask <trademark>Google</trademark> "
#| "to search for items related to &konqueror;."
msgid ""
"For example, entering <userinput>gg:konqueror</userinput> into the Location "
